<h2>Order Confirmation</h2>

<p>Dear <%= @order.buyer.name %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for your order! We are happy to confirm that your order has been successfully placed.</p>

<p>Your order details are as follows:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Order Number:</strong> <%= @order.id %></li>
  <li><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  <li><strong>Shipping Address:</strong> <%= @order.address %></li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>The <%= Rails.application.class.module_parent_name %> Team</p>
